===United Kingdom===
A number of flags for localities in the United Kingdom (primarily [[Scotland]]) are based on Nordic cross designs, intended to reflect the Scandinavian heritage introduced to the British Isles during the [[Viking Age]] and through the [[High Middle Ages]].{{citation needed|date=November 2018}}

